title: Welcome to My Blog
description: Welcome to my blog! This is the first post so don't expect to much. I've put about 24 hours into designing and compiling this website from multiple sources across the internet.

body.raw:
Welcome to my blog! This is the first post so don't expect to much. I've put about 24 hours into designing and compiling this website from multiple sources across the internet.

Here are a few of my references for how I made this blog:
- [TailwindCSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
- [Next.js and Contentlayer static blog guide - DEV Community](https://dev.to/seankerwin/nextjs-and-contentlayer-static-markdown-blog-guide-2n8k)
- [I Built A Snappy Static Full-text Search with WebAssembly, Rust, Next.js, and Xor Filters](https://dawchihliou.github.io/articles/i-built-a-snappy-full-text-search-with-webassembly-rust-nextjs-and-xor-filters)
- [Contentlayer](https://www.contentlayer.dev/docs)
- [Next.JS](https://nextjs.org/docs/getting-started)
- [How to build the static blog with Content layer, markdown, and nextjs?](https://medium.com/nextjs/how-to-build-the-static-blog-with-content-layer-markdown-and-nextjs-29f6ac93d06)

If you would like to know more about me feel free to checkout my socials on the lest side of the screen or above if you are on mobile.
